Class PreparedPolygonCovers

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.prep.PreparedPolygonPredicate
      com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.prep.AbstractPreparedPolygonContains
          com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.prep.PreparedPolygonCovers
public class PreparedPolygonCovers
extends AbstractPreparedPolygonContains

Computes the covers spatial relationship predicate for a PreparedPolygon relative to all other Geometry classes. Uses short-circuit tests and indexing to improve performance.

It is not possible to short-circuit in all cases, in particular in the case where the test geometry touches the polygon linework. In this case full topology must be computed.

Author:
Martin Davis
